[[fr:AutresModificationsRÃ©centes]]

Here are alternatives for the RecentChanges link which you might
want to bookmark, if you are a
RecentChangesJunkie.

* [EmacsWiki:action=rc;showedit=0 Show latest major changes] -- the default list of recent changes.
* [EmacsWiki:action=rc;showedit=1 Show latest changes] -- including minor ones.
* [EmacsWiki:action=rc;all=1;showedit=1;days=3 Show all changes for the last three days] -- including every single change.
* [EmacsWiki:action=rc;all=1;showedit=1;days=1 Show all changes for today]
* [EmacsWiki:action=rc;all=1;showedit=1;days=1;newtop=0 Show all changes for today, most recent last] -- ''Doesn't work''
* [http://www.emacswiki.org/elisp/changelog.html Show changes to Elisp files and packages]
* RecentChangesMinusIcicles for strategies to avoid recent changes entries related to [[Icicles]].

Language specific -- languages are identified using an implementation similar to GuessBufferLanguage.

* [EmacsWiki:action=rc;lang=en Show latest major changes to English pages]
* [EmacsWiki:action=rc;lang=es Show latest major changes to Spanish pages]
* [EmacsWiki:action=rc;lang=de Show latest major changes to German pages]
* [EmacsWiki:action=rc;lang=fr Show latest major changes to French pages]
* [EmacsWiki:action=rc;lang=it Show latest major changes to Italian pages]

See LanguageIdentification for more.

If you can integrate RSS feeds (see RichSiteSummary) into
your browser (or if you use NewsTicker):

* [EmacsWiki:action=rss RSS feed with major changes only, most recent first] -- see WikiRss for more.
* [EmacsWiki:action=rss;rsslimit=all RSS feed with major changes only]
* [EmacsWiki:action=rss;newtop=0;rsslimit=all RSS feed with major changes only, most recent last] -- ''Doesn't work''
* [EmacsWiki:action=rss;all=1;days=3;showedit=1;rsslimit=all RSS feed for the last three days with all changes] -- including every single change.
